Usage: generate_power_up_report [-help] -output_directory <string>
                                -state_directory <string> [-switch_net <string>]

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
-output_directory <string>              # output directory (string, required)
-state_directory <string>               # state directory (string, required)
-switch_net <string>                    # <switch power net name>
                                        # (string, optional)